{"title":"Joyi Zhang","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Joyi Zhang","image":"files/profile_pic.jpg","about":{"template":"trestles","links":[{"icon":"envelope","href":"mailto:joz021@ucsd.edu"},{"icon":"linkedin","href":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/joyi-zhang-731331341"}]},"toc":false},"headingText":"Tools","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\nMS in Business Analytics @ UCSD | Data Analyst | Business Analytics | Dashboarding & Reporting | Python | Consulting, Supply Chain & Finance\n\nFun fact: I write novels, debate my dog's opinions, and dance in heels.\n\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"tools-grid\">\n  <div class=\"tools-row\">\n    <span class=\"tools-cat-label\">Languages</span>\n    <div class=\"tools-chips\">\n      <span class=\"chip chip-lang\">Python</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-lang\">SQL</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-lang\">R</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"tools-row\">\n    <span class=\"tools-cat-label\">Analytics &amp; BI</span>\n    <div class=\"tools-chips\">\n      <span class=\"chip chip-bi\">Tableau</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-bi\">Power BI</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-bi\">Excel / VBA</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-bi\">Google Analytics</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-bi\">Salesforce</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"tools-row\">\n    <span class=\"tools-cat-label\">Data Engineering</span>\n    <div class=\"tools-chips\">\n      <span class=\"chip chip-eng\">PySpark</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-eng\">AWS</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-eng\">Databricks</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-eng\">BigQuery</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-eng\">ETL</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-eng\">Git</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n## Experience\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"timeline\">\n\n  <!-- Thermo Fisher Scientific -->\n  <div class=\"tl-item tl-c1\">\n    <div class=\"tl-dot\">\n      <img src=\"files/logos/thermo-fisher.png\" alt=\"TF\"\n           onerror=\"this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\">\n      <span class=\"tl-init\">TF</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tl-body\">\n      <div class=\"tl-header\">\n        <div class=\"tl-meta\">\n          <span class=\"tl-org\">Thermo Fisher Scientific</span>\n          <span class=\"tl-title\">Data Analyst (Capstone) · San Diego, CA</span>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"tl-date\">Feb 2026 – Present</span>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"tl-bullets\">\n        <li>Developed a supply chain risk early-flagging framework via Python-SQL based ETL workflows to identify key drivers of OTTP% misses, leveraging query-sourced order, inventory, ATP, and pharma backlog trends across SKUs</li>\n        <li>Partnered with cross-functional business stakeholders to validate root-cause and ML indicators, translate insights into operational recommendations and deploy the solution in Databricks and PowerBI for sustainable decision support</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Checkit Analytics -->\n  <div class=\"tl-item tl-c2\">\n    <div class=\"tl-dot\">\n      <img src=\"files/logos/checkit.png\" alt=\"CK\"\n           onerror=\"this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\">\n      <span class=\"tl-init\">CK</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tl-body\">\n      <div class=\"tl-header\">\n        <div class=\"tl-meta\">\n          <span class=\"tl-org\">Checkit Analytics</span>\n          <span class=\"tl-title\">Digital Marketing Intern · San Diego, CA</span>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"tl-date\">Feb 2026 – Present</span>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"tl-bullets\">\n        <li>Developed a cross-channel marketing machine learning framework by wrangling data using Python, identifying top-performing content on views, engagement, and subscriber conversion</li>\n        <li>Built BI-style analyses to segment user behavior and identify high-performing content drivers</li>\n        <li>Designed a social media content intelligence pipeline using Claude API to uncover high-performing messaging patterns and accelerate product experimentation (A/B test), improving content prototype usability by ~30%</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Fudan AI3 -->\n  <div class=\"tl-item tl-c3\">\n    <div class=\"tl-dot\">\n      <span class=\"tl-init\" style=\"display:flex\">AI³</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tl-body\">\n      <div class=\"tl-header\">\n        <div class=\"tl-meta\">\n          <span class=\"tl-org\">Fudan University AI³ Institute × Alibaba Koubei</span>\n          <span class=\"tl-title\">Data Scientist Intern · Shanghai, China</span>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"tl-date\">Apr 2025 – Jun 2025</span>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"tl-bullets\">\n        <li>Co-built a retail traffic forecasting system using O2O data (~1M records, 2,000 merchants), supporting inventory and staffing decisions and reducing an estimated 14% operational costs</li>\n        <li>Cleaned and engineered production-ready time-series datasets in Python by performing EDA, joins, quality checks and feature engineering to ensure reliable downstream machine learning analytics</li>\n        <li>Delivered merchant-facing dashboards in PowerBI by integrating demand signals with contextual factors (weather, local events), informing targeted operational strategies and identifying city-level customer lifecycle values</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- S&P Global -->\n  <div class=\"tl-item tl-c4\">\n    <div class=\"tl-dot\">\n      <img src=\"files/logos/sp-global.png\" alt=\"S&amp;P\"\n           onerror=\"this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\">\n      <span class=\"tl-init\">S&amp;P</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tl-body\">\n      <div class=\"tl-header\">\n        <div class=\"tl-meta\">\n          <span class=\"tl-org\">S&amp;P Global</span>\n          <span class=\"tl-title\">Consultant Intern, Mobility Group · Shanghai, China</span>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"tl-date\">May 2024 – Nov 2024</span>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"tl-bullets\">\n        <li>Conducted 10+ data-driven market and strategy studies on EV sector, covering OEM product strategies, platform roadmaps, net growth and demand outlook, delivering actionable insights via decks and Tableau dashboards</li>\n        <li>Used SQL-based ad hoc analysis to maintain and report recurring competitive intelligence datasets, performing reconciliation to ensure data accuracy and consistency across reporting cycles</li>\n        <li>Collected powertrain data (50K+ records) via Python by integrating APIs and web scraping, standardizing outputs into ESG metrics, and working cross-functionally with global teams to support a shared assessment database for research</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- East West Bank -->\n  <div class=\"tl-item tl-c1\">\n    <div class=\"tl-dot\">\n      <img src=\"files/logos/east-west-bank.png\" alt=\"EW\"\n           onerror=\"this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\">\n      <span class=\"tl-init\">EW</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tl-body\">\n      <div class=\"tl-header\">\n        <div class=\"tl-meta\">\n          <span class=\"tl-org\">East West Bank</span>\n          <span class=\"tl-title\">FP&amp;A Intern · Shanghai, China</span>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"tl-date\">Nov 2023 – Mar 2024</span>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"tl-bullets\">\n        <li>Maintained Asset-Liability Committee reports and Excel frameworks to track monthly accounting trends, providing directors with performance reports in PPT</li>\n        <li>Tracked budget execution, cost ratios, and loan KPIs by unit using Excel formulas (VLOOKUP) and pivot tables, creating dynamic visualizations to help VPs interpret spending patterns</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n```\n\n## Education\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"timeline\">\n\n  <!-- UCSD MSBA -->\n  <div class=\"tl-item tl-c1\">\n    <div class=\"tl-dot\">\n      <img src=\"files/logos/ucsd.png\" alt=\"UC\"\n           onerror=\"this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\">\n      <span class=\"tl-init\">UC</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tl-body\">\n      <div class=\"tl-header\">\n        <div class=\"tl-meta\">\n          <span class=\"tl-org\">UC San Diego, Rady School of Management</span>\n          <span class=\"tl-title\">M.S. Business Analytics</span>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"tl-date\">Aug 2025 – Jun 2026</span>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"tl-bullets\">\n        <li>GPA: 3.84 / 4.0</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Fudan University -->\n  <div class=\"tl-item tl-c2\">\n    <div class=\"tl-dot\">\n      <img src=\"files/logos/fudan.png\" alt=\"FDU\"\n           onerror=\"this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\">\n      <span class=\"tl-init\">FDU</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tl-body\">\n      <div class=\"tl-header\">\n        <div class=\"tl-meta\">\n          <span class=\"tl-org\">Fudan University, Shanghai</span>\n          <span class=\"tl-title\">B.A. Literature, Minor in Finance</span>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"tl-date\">Sep 2021 – Jun 2025</span>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"tl-bullets\">\n        <li>GPA: 3.51 / 4.0</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n```\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\nMS in Business Analytics @ UCSD | Data Analyst | Business Analytics | Dashboarding & Reporting | Python | Consulting, Supply Chain & Finance\n\nFun fact: I write novels, debate my dog's opinions, and dance in heels.\n\n## Tools\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"tools-grid\">\n  <div class=\"tools-row\">\n    <span class=\"tools-cat-label\">Languages</span>\n    <div class=\"tools-chips\">\n      <span class=\"chip chip-lang\">Python</span>\n      <span class=\"chip chip-lang\">SQL</span>